Description

Incorporated in 2007 with headquarters in Hawalli, Kuwait. Al Argan Gulf Real Estate Services is a shareholding company operating within the Real Estate sector. The company specializes in providing real estate development, leasing and property management services. The company is a subsidiary of Al Argan International Real Estate KSCP in Kuwait. Al Argan Gulf Real Estate Services is a private company.
